flavor_text_entries.gold:
The scent of
spices comes from
around its neck. Somehow, sniffing
it makes you want
to fight.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
A spicy aroma ema­
nates from around
its neck. The aroma acts as a
stimulant to re­
store health.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
The scent that
wafts from the
leaves on its neck causes anyone who
smells it to
become energetic.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
BAYLEEF’s neck is ringed by curled-up
leaves. Inside each tubular leaf is a
small shoot of a tree. The fragrance of this shoot makes
people peppy.
